data.description: Beautiful, Move-in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage pool home, with an oversized den/office that could easily be used as a 4th bedroom.  Home is located in the desirable community of Cedar Grove at The Woodlands with a Community Pool, Playground, Convenient Location, Public Water & Sewer & No Flood Insurance Required!  Home was built in 2017 and backs up to a private preserve. HEATED Pool and Solar System were added in 2020. The property offers an open layout with upgraded tray ceilings in both the living room and master bedroom, shiplap accent wall in the living room, granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, wood kitchen cabinets with large island that is great for entertaining, hurricane shutters and wood shelving in the garage. The monthly HOA dues include, lawn maintenance and care of the common grounds.
